       fil-fit-ing-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo funzione 'GS' del modulo 'mfatfit0'    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero periodi di riferimento           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rr-num-pdr           =    11 or
                     rr-num-pdr           =    12
                     move  02             to   w-mod-fat-fit-npr
           else      move  rr-num-pdr     to   w-mod-fat-fit-npr      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 1. periodo, data min                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p1d-min           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p1i      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 1. periodo, data max                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p1d-max           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p1f      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 2. periodo, data min                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p2d-min           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p2i      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 2. periodo, data max                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p2d-max           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p2f      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 3. periodo, data min                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p3d-min           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p3i      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * 3. periodo, data max                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rr-p3d-max           to   w-mod-fat-fit-p3f      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiamata modulo                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   mod-fat-fit-gts-000  thru mod-fat-fit-gts-999    .
       fil-fit-ing-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Lettura sequenziale archivio [fit]                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       fil-fit-get-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
