                     move  spaces         to   srt-k02-mne-cli
                     move  zero           to   srt-k02-flg-zod
                     move  zero           to   srt-k02-cod-cli
                     move  spaces         to   srt-k02-dpz-cli
                     go to cmp-srt-rec-400.
